<td colspan="2" class="fn summary" style="text-align:center; font-size: 125%; font-weight: bold; text-align:center; font-size:125%;"><b>Vandana Shiva</b></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td colspan="2" class="" style="text-align:center; padding:4pt; line-height:1.25em; text-align:center; font-size:8pt;"><a href="/wiki/File:Vandana_Shiva,_environmentalist,_at_Rishikesh,_2007.jpg" class="image" title="Vandana Shiva, environmentalist, at Rishikesh, 2007.jpg"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/18/Vandana_Shiva%2C_environmentalist%2C_at_Rishikesh%2C_2007.jpg/225px-Vandana_Shiva%2C_environmentalist%2C_at_Rishikesh%2C_2007.jpg" width="225" height="254" border="0" /></a><br />
<div style="padding-top:2pt;"></div>
</td>
